latestIgtvVideos.title: Thank you @hiphopskincare for such a thoughtful 📦❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Given the situation where we are all adapting to a few new routines, where we also have to find out something to keep ourselves well groomed as it’s no more safe to visit salons for waxing and stuff. Hence, I’m so glad that @hiphopskincare sent in this really thoughtful PR package with the most essential stuff when it comes to grooming. In the 📦 there’s a Charcoal Nose Strips (long time favourite), Chocolate easy to use Wax Strips, Facial Wax Strips, Hair removal creams in two different variants Argan oil and Charcoal. Thank you once again ❤️📦 .
